high_descs: Go up to the sink then turn left and go to the chair at the end of the mat then turn right then left to go around the chair and go to the table
Pick up the lettuce closest to you from the table
Turn around and take a step then turn right and go to the fridge
Put the lettuce in the fridge to chill then take the lettuce out of the fridge
Turn around and then turn left and go to the sink and turn to face the sink
Put the lettuce in the sink on the left
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in a sink

high_descs: Walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk across the room to the right side of the round black table.
Pick up the closest head of lettuce off of the round black table.
Walk up to the fridge behind you.
Put the head of lettuce in the fridge then close the door, after a couple seconds take the now chilled head of lettuce out of the fridge.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the chilled head of lettuce in the leftmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room and turn left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the lettuce on the kitchen table.
Turn around to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the sink.
Place the head of lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move a head of lettuce from the kitchen table to the sink.
